				<h2> The Bund Summit 2015 on Internet Finance Agenda</h2>
				<p> Internet finance has been growing rapidly in China and drawing attention from
					around the globe. To address the development and challenges facing the
					industry, Shanghai Finance Institute (SFI) and LendIt will jointly host The
					Bund Summit 2015 on Internet Finance &amp; SFI Annual Conference. The theme will be
					"Internet Finance: Innovation, Risks and Regulation". Financial innovators,
					investors and pioneers will gather to discuss industry trends, learn from
					market leaders, form key business alliances, and showcase industry-moving
					products and services. </p>
				<p>
					This-500 person conference in Shanghai has become the most influential Chinese conference focused on online lending. We will host many members of the top regulatory bodies including the PBoC, CRBC, CSRC, and CIRC. In addition, we will have keynotes from the China Investment Corp, China's largest sovereign wealth fund, and Alibaba's ZhaoCaiBao unit of Ant Financial, their P2P division, among others.
				</p>
